components.description:
An emoji version of the digit 1, created via a variation selector.

Not given emoji presentation on Apple or Microsoft devices, or on platforms such as Facebook and Twitter / X. Microsoft did previously support this emoji within Windows 8 and Windows 10.

apple_vendor_description: The keycap digit one emoji on Apple devices presents a crisp, white numeral '1' within a vibrant blue square, rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading.  Its soft rounded edges and subtle gradients give it a clean, modern aesthetic, perfectly conveying the concept of being first or representing a singular item.  This emoji is ideal for indicating ranking, a primary choice, or simply the number one in digital conversations on Apple devices.
